Package: MixLS
Type: Package
Title: Mixed-Effects Location Scale Modeling
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Jianan Rui <jiananrui@uchicao.edu>
Maintainer: Jianan Rui <jiananrui@uchicao.edu>
Description: This package fits mixed-effects location scale models using a three-stage estimation procedure, allowing for both within-subject and between-subject variance heterogeneity.
